OL,3,CIs the government's decision on Waspi
OL,4,Cwomen compensation brave or
OL,5,Cshortsighted?
OL,7,FThis is not the first time that the
OL,8,FStarmer government has chosen to
OL,9,Falienate an important group of
OL,10,Fpensioner voters, ITV News' Sangita
OL,11,FLal and Robert Peston report
OL,13,FI have a few thoughts about the
OL,14,Fgovernment's refusal to pay
OL,15,Fcompensation to Waspi women for the
OL,16,Ffailure of previous administrations to
OL,17,Fproperly inform them about the
OL,18,Fsignificant increases to the state
OL,19,Fpension age for women.
