OL,3,CIs the government's decision on Waspi
OL,4,Cwomen compensation brave or
OL,5,Cshortsighted?
OL,7,FFirst, if this proven
OL,8,Fmaladministration had been by a bank
OL,9,For private sector institution, my
OL,10,Fhunch is that regulators and courts
OL,11,Fwould have compelled the payment of
OL,12,Fsignificant compensation with minimal
OL,13,Frequirement for claimants to prove
OL,14,Fdirect loss (think of the colossal
OL,15,Fsums banks paid out for mis-selling
OL,16,FPPI insurance).
OL,18,FThe ability of the government to just
OL,19,Fsay no is a striking contrast.
