OL,3,CIs the government's decision on Waspi
OL,4,Cwomen compensation brave or
OL,5,Cshortsighted?
OL,7,FSecond, the emotional distress and
OL,8,Fhardship suffered by many older women
OL,9,Fwas accepted by the ombudsman, but is
OL,10,Fnot deemed by the work and pensions
OL,11,Fsecretary to merit financial
OL,12,Fcompensation.
OL,14,FThird, this is the second time in its
OL,15,Fshort life that the Starmer government
OL,16,Fhas chosen to alienate an important
OL,17,Fgroup of pensioner voters.
OL,19,FThis is either brave and farsighted or
OL,20,Fnot.
